<h1>Recipe Finder App</h1>
<p>Created by <%= link_to("Diogo Matsubara", "https://www.linkedin.com/in/diogo-matsubara-699314/") %> for Coursera's <%= link_to("Ruby on Rails: An Introduction", "https://www.coursera.org/learn/ruby-on-rails-intro") %></p>

<p> Fill in a search term directly in the URL (Ex. <%= link_to("?search=mocha", "/?search=mocha") %>). Default is to search for <b>chocolate</b>.</p>

<table border="1">
  <tr>
    <th>Image</th>
    <th>Title</th>
    <th>Social Rank</th>
  </tr>
  <% @recipes.each do |recipe| %>
    <tr class=<%= cycle("even", "odd") %>>
      <td><%= link_to(image_tag(recipe["image_url"], size: "100x100"), recipe["f2f_url"]) %></td>
      <td><%= link_to(sanitize(recipe["title"]), recipe["f2f_url"]) %></td>
      <td><%= recipe["social_rank"] %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
